rows.label: qst701110_msg0001
rows.name:
Ohohoho... It looks like everything
worked out quite well, I see.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, young lady? How about you?
Do you know yet what you want to
accomplish?

rows.label: qst701110_msg0003
rows.name:
No... No, I don't quite yet.
But I know I'll be thinking about it.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0004
rows.name:
Up until now I was focused on survival.
That didn't leave much time for setting
goals and personal objectives...

rows.label: qst701110_msg0005
rows.name:
I see...
Well, there's no shame in that.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0006
rows.name:
Whichever way the world turns, I hope
you'll always stay true to yourself.
One must be strong, yet supple.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0007
rows.name:
That phrasing...
It could apply to water, no? It bends
around obstacles, yet does not break.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0008
rows.name:
Truly yours is a most interesting mind!
I do wish we could make time to talk
at our leisure.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0011
rows.name:
You are not a mere instrument for
responding to my orders and demands.
You can do as you please.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0012
rows.name:
Exactly, Wadatsumi.
His Majesty can well make do
with just me for a time.

rows.label: qst701110_msg0014
rows.name:
Wadatsumi, was it? Is it perhaps that
you don't believe we could become
fast friends?

rows.label: qst701110_msg0016
rows.name:
Let us retire now, for there is much
to speak of...kind sir.
